Module chav1961.purelib

Package chav1961.purelib.nanoservice.interfaces

This package contains an API to use with NanoService implementations. It contains a NanoService interface definition and a set of annotations to use in the pluggable processing classes.

Since:
0.0.3
Author:
Alexander Chernomyrdin aka chav1961
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MethodExecutor
    This interface is an internal interface for NanoServiceFactory implementation.
    MultipartContent  
    NanoService
    This interface describes any Nano services in the Pure Library.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    QueryType
    This enumeration describes type of HTTP request
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    FromBody
    This annotation marks method parameter containing request body.
    FromHeader
    This annotation marks method parameter containing request header.
    FromPath
    This annotation marks method parameter containing request URI path.
    FromQuery
    This annotation marks method parameter containing request URI query.
    HeaderName  
    Path
    This annotation marks request URI path pattern matches to the given method call, and query type to accept.
    RootPath
    This annotation marks request URI path prefix for all the methods of the given class.
    ToBody
    This annotation marks method parameter to keep response body.
    ToHeader
    This annotation marks method parameter to keep response header.
